Chuwojineun nalssi
Georie modeun namnyeodeureun jeonbu kkyeoango nalli
Yeojeonhi saljjak tteoreojyeoseo geotgo inneun uri
Nae soneun ni soneuro umjigidaga meomchit tto meomchit tto meomchit

